{"tid":1852832,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"旺角一藥房負責人被捕 涉賣虛假生產日期口罩","createTime":"2020-01-30T15:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T15:53:42.000Z","uid":326897,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"66e91d638d3610776625f96930f1796731e15bd4","tid":1852832,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:39:49.000Z","msg":"旺角一藥房負責人被捕 涉賣虛假生產日期口罩<br />\n2020-01-30 HKT 22:40<br />\n<br />\n旺角一藥房負責人被捕 涉賣虛假生產日期口罩<br />\n海關在旺角奶路臣街「信生中西大藥房」，拘捕一名27歲藥房負責人，指他涉嫌售賣虛假生產日期的口罩，涉及6萬8000個。<br />\n<br />\n該批口罩的包裝盒上寫有「KLEAN MASK」，生產日期為2020年3月，批次為「LKM9034」，未有產地聲稱。每盒口罩有50個，索價280元。海關檢走有關口罩並送往化驗，以確定有關口罩的安全效能及追查來源。<br />\n<br />\n海關商品說明調查科總貿易管制主任佘慧嫺表示，現時未知道有多少涉事口罩流入市面，仍在追查中。另外，被問到潛在出現的二手口罩問題，她表示，會進行試購行動，呼籲商戶不要混水摸魚，消費者應光顧信譽良好的商戶，並應細心留意口罩的包裝及有關說明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505742-20200130.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505742-20200130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinAxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=27f60f5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505742-20200130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1559ca5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505742-20200130.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n2020年3月, 我重以為係有效日期, 未來口罩嚟啦"},{"pid":"89ef8f8738128c9195d0f308c7e9e316cbf3da8b","tid":1852832,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"抵撚死on9佬"},{"pid":"757404e09e4a804f864c3fe1a0b323d7372d918b","tid":1852832,"uid":54031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db24eb60f4874b1043804315bcda5b67a4ad945c","tid":1852832,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c389802fd09e7b3203397a74d1cbdd1143c647c","tid":1852832,"uid":1224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:45:23.000Z","msg":"裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c716920aa7f43eda3319bb0001437f08dff050","tid":1852832,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有線個件?"},{"pid":"e94f9dd5b7879729b3dac90b3b2d014e2bd35327","tid":1852832,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:47:51.000Z","msg":"2020年3月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd921e11d44f62036b176f7b460cdf5da353ea45","tid":1852832,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"根本係d新派藥房搞屎棍. 唔做香港人生意.<br />\n炒口罩仲覺得啱...<br />\n<br />\n舊派藥房, 老人家多. 有人情味d. 熟客仲會留貨比人"},{"pid":"aabf2ced9887c00880e78c04acbc887c6b396c9e","tid":1852832,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"哩啲係未叫做賊都做得蠢撚過人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}